cloud-white-description =
    Cloud White is a clean, bright light theme for the FreeSynergy desktop.

    It uses white and soft gray backgrounds with sky blue accent colors and
    dark charcoal text. Panels are crisp and borderless. Cloud White is designed
    for well-lit environments and users who prefer working in light mode.

cloud-white-features =
    - White and soft gray backgrounds
    - Sky blue accent color
    - Dark charcoal text for high readability
    - Crisp, minimal panel style
    - Designed for bright, well-lit environments
    - Light mode counterpart to Midnight Blue
